{"body": [{"indent": 0, "text": ["Sculpt"], "type": "title", "extent": [32, 43], "level": 0}, {"indent": 0, "type": "summary", "extent": [43, 105], "text": ["Lets you interactively reshape a surface by brushing."]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [105, 280], "text": ["The deform mode lets you push or pull the geometry along its normals and the smooth mode smooths out the geometry. This tool is useful for adding detail to ", {"text": ["models"], "fullpath": "/model/index", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/model/"}, "."]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [463, 683], "text": ["When you select a subset of points, the ", {"text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/SOP/sculpt", "scheme": "Icon", "type": "link", "value": "SOP/sculpt"}, {"text": ["Sculpt"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/sculpt", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/sculpt"}, " tool will only be able to modify the selected points. The unselected points will be protected from ", {"text": ["brushing"], "fullpath": "/basics/brush", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/basics/brush"}, "."]}], "indent": 4, "text": [{"text": ["Select"], "fullpath": "/basics/select", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/basics/select"}, " the object you want to sculpt, ", {"text": ["or"], "type": "em"}, " in ", {"text": ["component mode"], "fullpath": "/basics/select", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/basics/select"}, ", select a subset of the points in an object."], "extent": [311, 463], "blevel": 6, "type": "ord"}, {"indent": 4, "blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "extent": [683, 774], "text": ["Click the ", {"text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/SOP/sculpt", "scheme": "Icon", "type": "link", "value": "SOP/sculpt"}, " ", {"text": ["Sculpt"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/sculpt", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/sculpt"}, " tool on the ", {"text": ["Model"], "type": "ui"}, " tab."]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 8, "blevel": 10, "type": "bullet", "extent": [810, 960], "text": ["Shift-drag to change the size of the brush, or use the ", {"text": ["Radius"], "type": "ui"}, " control on the operation toolbar (across the top of the viewer)."]}, {"indent": 8, "blevel": 10, "type": "bullet", "extent": [960, 1083], "text": ["Right click to assign operations to ", {"keys": ["LMB"], "text": null, "type": "keys"}, " and ", {"keys": ["MMB"], "text": null, "type": "keys"}, ", change the brush shape, and set other options."]}, {"indent": 8, "blevel": 10, "type": "bullet", "extent": [1083, 1421], "text": [{"text": ["FD"], "type": "ui"}, " on the toolbar controls the amount of displacement caused by brushing with ", {"keys": ["LMB"], "text": null, "type": "keys"}, ". ", {"text": ["BD"], "type": "ui"}, " controls the amount caused by brushing with ", {"keys": ["MMB"], "text": null, "type": "keys"}, ". These are the same as the parameters in the ", {"text": ["LMB Displacement"], "type": "ui"}, " and ", {"text": ["MMB Displacement"], "type": "ui"}, " sub-tabs of the ", {"text": ["Operation"], "type": "ui"}, " tab in the ", {"text": ["parameter editor"], "fullpath": "/ref/panes/parms", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/ref/panes/parms"}, "."]}, {"indent": 8, "blevel": 10, "type": "bullet", "extent": [1421, 1647], "text": [{"text": ["Opacity"], "type": "ui"}, " controls how much deformation or smoothing the tool will do with each brush-stroke. This is the same as the ", {"text": ["Opacity"], "type": "ui"}, " parameter on the ", {"text": ["Brush"], "type": "ui"}, " tab in the ", {"text": ["parameter editor"], "fullpath": "/ref/panes/parms", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/ref/panes/parms"}, "."]}, {"indent": 8, "blevel": 10, "type": "bullet", "extent": [1647, 1768], "text": ["Drag across the surface with ", {"keys": ["LMB"], "text": null, "type": "keys"}, " or ", {"keys": ["MMB"], "text": null, "type": "keys"}, " to perform the assigned operation on the selected points."]}], "container": true, "type": "bullet_group"}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Do any of the following:"], "extent": [774, 810], "blevel": 6, "type": "ord"}], "container": true, "type": "ord_group"}, {"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [1768, 1810], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/images/shelf/sculpt.png", "scheme": "Image", "type": "link", "value": "/images/shelf/sculpt.png"}]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [1819, 1986], "text": ["The ", {"text": ["brush"], "fullpath": "/basics/brush", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/basics/brush"}, " casts through the surface and sometimes you may find that strokes on the surface deform points on the opposite side of the surface."]}, {"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [1986, 2214], "text": ["You can minimize this by enabling the ", {"text": ["Depth"], "type": "ui"}, " parameter on the ", {"text": ["Brush"], "type": "ui"}, " tab in the ", {"text": ["parameter editor"], "fullpath": "/ref/panes/parms", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/ref/panes/parms"}, ". The ", {"text": ["Depth"], "type": "ui"}, " values limit how far ", {"text": ["above"], "type": "em"}, " and ", {"text": ["below"], "type": "em"}, " the surface the brush will cast."]}, {"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [2214, 2504], "text": ["You can copy the ", {"text": ["Radius"], "type": "ui"}, " parameter and paste it as a relative reference into both ", {"text": ["Depth"], "type": "ui"}, " fields to create a spherical/cubical (depending on brush shape) brush. This is usually sufficient to eliminate problems casting through, unless you are using a large brush size."]}], "indent": 4, "role": "item", "type": "tip", "extent": [1810, 1819]}], "container": true, "role": "item_group", "type": "tip_group"}], "indent": 0, "level": 2, "text": ["Using Sculpt"], "extent": [280, 311], "container": true, "type": "h", "id": "includeme"}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [2504, 2595], "text": ["For specific parameter help see the ", {"text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/SOP/sculpt", "scheme": "Icon", "type": "link", "value": "SOP/sculpt"}, " ", {"text": ["Sculpt"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/sculpt", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/sculpt"}, " node help."]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [2595, 2667], "text": ["For general brush information see the ", {"text": ["brush tool"], "fullpath": "/basics/brush", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/basics/brush"}, " help."]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 4, "blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "extent": [2676, 2731], "text": [{"text": ["Capture Layer Paint"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/capturelayerpaint", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/capturelayerpaint"}]}, {"indent": 4, "blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "extent": [2731, 2758], "text": [{"text": ["Comb"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/comb", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/comb"}]}, {"indent": 4, "blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "extent": [2758, 2787], "text": [{"text": ["Paint"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/paint", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/paint"}]}, {"indent": 4, "blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "extent": [2787, 2821], "text": [{"text": ["UV Brush"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/uvbrush", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/uvbrush"}]}], "container": true, "type": "bullet_group"}], "indent": 0, "level": 1, "text": "Related", "role": "section", "extent": [2667, 2676], "container": true, "type": "related_section", "id": "related"}], "summary": ["Lets you interactively reshape a surface by brushing."], "type": "root", "attrs": {"tags": "model", "icon": "SOP/sculpt"}, "title": ["Sculpt"]}